      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.On2ZrPJTe8FURsXY]{Operative Exploit}</p>\n<p>When a vehicle you’re in becomes broken, becomes wrecked, crashes, or takes collision damage, you can use a reaction to jump from the vehicle as though you had a running start. You halve any falling damage you might take from this jump. You can’t use this exploit if you’re currently benefiting from total cover inside a vehicle, and the GM might prohibit its use in other situations where you couldn’t feasibly reach and break free from a vehicle’s interior.</p>"
